NOTE [[割圓術始載於劉徽所著九章算術注]]

i have 1 num. called 1. name it [半徑].
mul [半徑] -> [半徑]. name it [半徑平方].

i have 1 func. name it [求小弦]. to perform. requires 2 num. called [裏觚之面]. called [輪數]. func begin.
	div [裏觚之面] -> 2.0. name it [半面].
	if [輪數] < 1.0 topic. return [裏觚之面] end.
	mul [半面] -> [半面]. name it [半面平方].
	sub [半徑平方] -> [半面平方]. take 1 -> call [平方根]. name it [股].
	sub [半徑] -> [股]. name it [小句].
	mul [小句] -> [小句]. add its -> [半面平方]. take 1 -> call [平方根]. name it [小弦].
	i have 2 num. called [小弦]. called sub [輪數] -> 1. take 2 -> call [求小弦]. return.
func end for [求小弦] func end.

NOTE [[輪數始於一]]
i have 1 func. name it [割圓術求圓率]. to perform. requires 1 num called [原輪數]. func begin.
	sub [原輪數] -> 1. name it [輪數].
	call [冪] <- 2 <- [輪數]. mul its -> 6. name it [觚數].
	call [求小弦] <- [半徑] <- [輪數]. name it [小弦].
	mul [小弦] -> [觚數]. name it [觚周].
	div [觚周] -> 2. mul its -> [半徑]. name it [觚冪].
	div [觚冪] -> [半徑平方]. name it [圓率].
	i have 3 str. called [[割圓]]. called [觚數]. called [[觚。所得圓率者。]]. print.
	i have 2 str. called [圓率]. called [[也。]]. print.
	return [圓率].
func end for [割圓術求圓率] func end.

call [割圓術求圓率] <- 10.
